                "accept_rate": 83
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1349321366,
            "creation_date": 1349321366,
            "body": "<p>One option (which might be overkill) would be for the components that are interested in the change in the value of <code>test1<\/code> and <code>test2<\/code> implement a <code>PropertyChangeListener<\/code> and register to listen for when the values of these properties are changed. <\/p>\n\n<p>Here is a <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/uiswing/events/propertychangelistener.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">tutorial<\/a>. <\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 12719884,
